    <item>
      <title>Margarita</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/margarita/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2018 14:28:50 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/margarita/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;If you’re feeling extra adventurous, muddle one or two slices of jalapeño in your shaker before adding the ingredients.&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz tequila&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz orange liqueur&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz lime juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¼ oz agave syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1 pinch of salt&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Shake vigorously with ice. Strain into a rocks glass filled with fresh ice.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Tabs vs. Spaces</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/tabs-vs-spaces/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 16 Jan 2018 12:27:00 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/tabs-vs-spaces/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;div class=&#34;recipe-intro p-summary&#34;&gt;It’s a programmer joke. I’m a nerd.&lt;/div&gt;


&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz tequila&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz Green Chartreuse&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;¾ oz lime juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz simple syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;pinch of salt&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;


&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
