    <item>
      <title>Blanc-arita</title>
      <link>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/blanc-arita/</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jan 2018 11:17:51 -0500</pubDate>
      
      <guid>https://sidecar.keithjgrant.com/drinks/blanc-arita/</guid>
      <description>
&lt;ul class=&#34;ingredients&#34;&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;2 oz silver tequila&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz blanc vermouth&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz lime juice&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;½ oz agave syrup&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class=&#34;p-ingredient&#34;&gt;1 dash orange bitters&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;



&lt;div class=&#34;instructions e-instructions&#34;&gt;
  Shake vigorously with ice. Strain into rocks glass over fresh ice.
&lt;/div&gt;


</description>
